FBIS3-43490 "drafr005_d_94013" FBIS-AFR-94-005 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Jan 1994 SOUTHERN AFRICA Mozambique Confined Soldiers Seeking Demobilization Plans MB0601184894 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network in Portuguese 1800 GMT 6 Jan 94 MB0601184894 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network Language: Portuguese Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Government soldiers confined to the Namialo assembly area in Nampula Province are demanding to know their future -- namely, whether they are to be demobilized or to join the future apolitical unified army. The 941 soldiers at Namialo confinement center want their situations defined so that they can start organizing their lives after many years of military life. [passage omitted]
